name: 8X8 Puller Over Yonder
description:
Get ready for this Awsome adventure and for any challenge.8X8 Puller Over Yonder is all about adventurous Transportation that’s full of hasty pace and adrenaline pumping thrills.Select your truck and complete the missions. Tear past the competition while expressing yourself with a variety of wild offloads.

Features:
* Many Levels With Stunning 3 Dimensional Graphics
* Intelligent Missions To Give You A Tough Competition.
* Crazy Addictive Experience.
* Smooth And Easy Game Play
* Environments That Keeps Changing
* Real Animations And Physics
